        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 600 S Curson St, Los Angeles, CA 90036 Located in the heart of LA’s Miracle Mile, Museum Terrace is the quintessential resort-style community offering the foremost luxury amenities and features. Ideally situated just steps from exceptional fine dining, parks, museums, the original Farmer's Market and The Grove, Museum Terrace is only 20 minutes from the beach and Downtown LA. Just around the corner you'll find LACMA and the La Brea Tar Pits. On Wednesday afternoons, enjoy local farmer's markets on Wilshire and Curson streets. Our stunning community features a sparkling pool, a relaxing jacuzzi, a fitness center, a resident lounge with complimentary Wi-Fi, covered and gated parking, and the friendliest staff you will ever encounter. Come in today so you can have your pick of one of our beautifully renovated luxury apartment homes. Museum Terrace truly provides everything you want for your Southern California lifestyle. After a long day at play, return to your upscale apartment Mid-Wilshire for a quiet evening with your beloved pet. Features Include: Multiple Laundry Facilities Fitness Center Guest Parking Resident Lounge w/ Free Wi-Fi Evening Courtesy Patrol Jetted Spa Jacuzzi Contact our office for pricing and details ParkingContact our office for pricing and details EV Charging Stations Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livegkmanagement.com/6rnewd7d/museum-terrace Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit. Contact us today for the most up to date information.",
