        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post 2001 Olympic Blvd, Santa Monica, CA 90404 Bedrooms:  0 Bathrooms:  1 Square Feet:  429 Rent Price:  1995 Our Santa Monica studio apartments are close to Santa Monica College, the Water Gardens, and the 10 Freeway, which makes commuting to school or work a breeze! A Ralphs supermarket is just a block away, while Bergamot Station and Virginia Avenue Park are also nearby. Experience modern income-restricted apartment living in Santa Monica. Most of our apartments are restricted to Moderate Income tenants, and the tenant rent portion and income limits of Moderate Income apartments shall not exceed: Maximum Rent: Maximum Income: Studio: $2120 1 person: $84,800 per year; 2 persons: $96,960 per year Studio: $2650 1 person: $106,000 per year; 2 persons: $121,200 per year (Rent and income limits provided are for general information purposes only and are subject to change). To verify income eligibility, you will be asked to provide proof of your income from all sources and assets. Please contact our leasing office for more information about the income and asset verification, as well as the application requirements for our Santa Monica affordable housing apartments. Professionally Managed by Cirrus Asset Management, Inc. CA- License # 01834798 Amenities Include: Stove Dishwasher Hardwood-Style Floors Stainless Steel Appliances Granite Counters Bike Racks Subterranean Gated Parking Available AC/Heat Laundry Facilities Control Access Entry Elevator On-Call Maintenance Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://cirrusmgmt.com/mkhvshif/olympic-lofts Pricing and availability are subject to change.",
