        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Flexible Lease Terms Available. Bright And Spacious Top Floor Studio Penthouse Apartment In Westwood. Close To Everything. 10930 Ashton Avenue Westwood, Los Angeles, California, 90024 Brentwood, West LA, Beverly Hills Studio penthouse apartment offers the following amenities: Stove And Oven Microwave Cable Available Dishwasher Central Air/Heating Refrigerator * Certain amenities are only available in select apartments Welcome to Ashton Towers, where sophisticated living meets the vibrant energy of Westwood. Nestled at 10930 Ashton Avenue in one of Los Angeles' most sought-after neighborhoods, this luxury apartment community redefines what it means to call Westwood home. Start your morning with a workout in our fully equipped fitness center, then unwind poolside as the afternoon unfolds. The rooftop terrace, complete with BBQ and grilling stations, will become one of your favorite spaces! This top floor studio penthouse apartment features a private balcony, laminate wood and tile floors, a kitchen equipped with a gas stove and oven, a dishwasher, and a refrigerator. We pride ourselves on ensuring residents only the best in apartment living. For appointment or for questions, call us at show contact info or visit http://www.AshtonTowers.com to apply. Community Amenities: Pool Assigned Parking Fitness Center Elevator Controlled Access BBQ/Grill Area Laundry Facilities Sauna EV Charging Stations Roof Terrace Disclaimer: Photos may not be of the exact apartment available and are intended to provide a general representation of the unit. Floor plans and square footages displayed are approximations and may vary between individual units. Rental rates, availability, lease terms, deposits, apartment features, amenities and specials are subject to change without notice. Terms may fluctuate based on qualifying standards.",
