        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Apply Now! Bachelor Westwood Apartment for this School Year! Close to Everything in Westwood! Flexible Lease Terms Available! Apply Now! Bachelor Westwood Apartment for this School Year! Close to Everything in Westwood! Features include central air/heat, kitchenette, quartz countertops, laminate floors and a mini fridge. Ace your lifestyle with stylish spaces, resident-focused perks, and a prime Westwood address at Midvale Court Apartments. We’ve curated amenities designed to bring joy to your days, from the ultimate relaxation combo of a sauna and spa to a rooftop terrace where many other facilities await. And because comfort goes beyond location, our apartments in Westwood, Los Angeles, boast updated appliances and must-have features like central air conditioning & heating. The city looks great from our Westwood apartments, and even better from the community terrace. There, you can fire up the grill for a delicious meal or take a refreshing dip in the shimmering pool. Looking to stay active? Hit your step goals in the fitness center. For added convenience, a controlled-access entrance, an elevator, laundry facilities, and assigned parking spots are all provided. Connectivity is second nature to our location, with easy access to bus transit, light rail stations, and Interstate 405. One moment, you’re in Sawtelle, the next, you’re navigating the Century City Business District, and by the end of the day, you’re unwinding with some retail therapy at Westfield Mall. Nestled in a prime area of Westwood, our apartments are near UCLA, as well as iconic landmarks like The Getty or Fox Studios. For appointment or for questions, call us today at show contact info or visit http://www.MidvaleCourt.com ! 1400 Midvale Avenue Westwood, Los Angeles, CA 90024 Phone: show contact info Website: http://www.MidvaleCourt.com Bachelor apartment offers the following features: Central Air/Heating Tile Flooring Laminate Flooring Quartz Countertops Mini Fridge Kitchenette * Certain amenities are only available in select apartments Community Amenities: Garage Business Center Stretch/Yoga room Controlled Access Laundry Facilities BBQ/Grill Area Roof Terrace Elevator Fitness Center EV Charging Station Sauna Assigned Parking Spa Pool Study Lounge Disclaimer: Photos may not be of the exact apartment available and are intended to provide a general representation of the unit. Floor plans and square footages displayed are approximations and may vary between individual units. Rental rates, availability, lease terms, deposits, apartment features, amenities and specials are subject to change without notice. Terms may fluctuate based on qualifying standards.",
