        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Flexible Lease Terms Available. Beautiful Top Floor 2 Bedroom 2 Bath Penthouse Los Angeles Home. Thoughtfully designed with comfort and convenience in mind, this top floor 2 bedroom 2 bath penthouse apartment features a wide array of stylishly efficient and stunningly appointed amenities including extra-high ceiling, a gourmet kitchen equipped with appliances, laminate wood/carpet flooring, granite countertops, private balcony, and more! At The Park Rochester, we offer residents everything they need for a lifestyle of comfort and convenience. Our residents are offered full access to all our exquisite community amenities. From the soothing spa/hot tub, fitness center, nearby parks, you'll find easy living with endless comforts and conveniences here at The Park Rochester. Perfectly situated in a very cosmopolitan neighborhood. Our convenient location puts you right where you want to be. Living at The Park Rochester, means you're close to public transportation, shopping, entertainment and all that Los Angeles has to offer. We pride ourselves on ensuring residents only the best in apartment living. For appointment or questions, call us at show contact info . 10969 Rochester Avenue Westwood, Los Angeles, California, 90024 Brentwood, West LA, Beverly Hills For more details and photos or to apply, visit our website at: http://www.ParkRochester.com This 2 bedroom offers the following amenities: Gas Stove/Oven Dishwasher Refrigerator Granite Countertops Laminate Wood Flooring in the Living Room Carpeted Bedrooms Balcony Tile Flooring Central Air/Heating Cozy Gas Fireplace * Certain amenities are only available in select apartments. The building amenities include the following features: Garage Assigned Parking Elevator Controlled Access Roof Terrace Fitness Center BBQ/Grill Area Laundry Facilities Sauna Spa Disclaimer: Photos may not be of the exact apartment available and are intended to provide a general representation of th