        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Flexible Lease Terms Available! Westwood 2 Bedroom 2 Bath Close to Everything. Ready for this School Year 2 bedroom apartment offers the following amenities: Cozy Gas Fireplace Microwave Stove and Oven Cable Available Dishwasher Central Air/Heating Quartz Countertops Refrigerator * Certain amenities are only available in select apartments Your search for Westwood LA apartments ends here. Inside your residence, central air conditioning ensures year-round comfort, while private balconies extend your living space into the California sunshine. Select apartments feature upgraded finishes that elevate everyday living. Start your morning with a workout in our fully equipped fitness center, then unwind poolside as the afternoon unfolds. The rooftop terrace, complete with BBQ and grilling stations, will become one of your favorite spaces! 10930 Ashton Avenue | Los Angeles, CA 90024 This 2 bedroom 2 bath apartment features a kitchen fully equipped with quartz countertops, a gas stove and oven, a dishwasher, and a refrigerator. Location places you at the intersection of convenience and culture. UCLA's campus lies within easy reach, making morning commutes nearly effortless for students and staff alike. West Los Angeles VA Medical Center and Ronald Reagan UCLA Medical Center provide nearby employment opportunities, while Wilshire Boulevard and Westwood Boulevard connect you to greater Los Angeles. When leisure calls, the Hammer Museum, IPIC Theaters, and Bristol Farms and Whole Foods await exploration, with Franklin Canyon Park and UCLA's Mathias Botanical Garden offering natural retreats minutes from your door. For appointment or for questions, call us today at show contact info or visit http://www.AshtonTowers.com . Community Amenities: Pool EV Charging Stations Elevator BBQ/Grill Area Roof Terrace Sauna Fitness Center Controlled Access Laundry Facilities Assigned Parking Disclaimer: Photos may not be of the exact apartment available and are intended to provide a general representation of the unit. Floor plans and square footages displayed are approximations and may vary between individual units. Rental rates, availability, lease terms, deposits, apartment features, amenities and specials are subject to change without notice. Terms may fluctuate based on qualifying standards.",
