        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post 10930 Ashton Avenue Los Angeles, CA 90024 Flexible Lease Terms Available. Apply now! 3 bedroom 3 bath apartment in great Westwood location! 3 bedroom apartment offers the following amenities: Dishwasher Private Balcony Central Air/Heating Cozy Gas Fireplace Gas Stove/Oven Laminate Floors Refrigerator * Certain amenities are only available in select apartments This 3 bedroom Westwood apartment features central air conditioning and heating, laminate floors, a fireplace and a private balcony. Kitchen is fully equipped with a gas stove/oven, a microwave, a dishwasher and a refrigerator. 10930 Ashton Avenue is a gorgeous 39-unit apartment complex centrally located in Westwood, a cosmopolitan, vibrant, and diverse community on the westside of Los Angeles, California. Minutes away to all popular Westside destinations including Armand Hammer Museum of Art & Cultural Center, UCLA, Getty Museum, Geffen Playhouse, Wadsworth Theatre. Fabulous restaurants and shopping, movie theatres, world class yoga, and public transportation are all at your fingertips. Community features include a swimming pool, a fitness center and gorgeous panoramic views of the Westwood skyline. For appointment or for questions, call us at show contact info . Community Amenities: Assigned Parking Fitness Center Elevator Sauna Pool EV Charging Stations Controlled Access Roof Terrace BBQ/Grill Area Laundry Facilities Visit our website at https://www.ashtontowers.com/ Disclaimer: Photos may not be of the exact apartment available and are intended to provide a general representation of the unit. Floor plans and square footages displayed are approximations and may vary between individual units. Rental rates, availability, lease terms, deposits, apartment features, amenities and specials are subject to change without notice. Terms may fluctuate based on qualifying standards.",
