        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Flexible Lease Terms Available. Westwood 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath Apartment in Prime Westwood Location. Close to UCLA. This Westwood 1-bedroom 1-bath apartment feature spacious living areas perfect for entertaining, a breakfast bar, a balcony, central air conditioning, hardwood laminate wood flooring, granite countertops and tiled flooring in bath and kitchen. Kitchen is equipped with a gas stove/oven, a dishwasher and a refrigerator. Our desirable studio, one-, and two-bedroom floor plans—including select townhome-style units—are designed with your lifestyle in mind. All apartments feature central air conditioning and heating, with most having stainless steel appliances and private balconies, while our on-site management and maintenance teams ensure a seamless living experience. Beyond your front door, enjoy community perks like a BBQ/grill area, laundry facilities, and a rooftop terrace perfect for relaxation. Perfectly situated in a very cosmopolitan neighborhood, our convenient location puts you within walking distance of everything in Westwood Village, just two blocks north of Wilshire and one block east of Westwood Boulevard, exactly where you want. Call us today at show contact info or visit http://www.TheHilgard.com. 972 Hilgard Avenue Westwood, Los Angeles, California, 90024 This 1 bedroom apartment offers the following amenities: Granite Countertops Microwave Gas Stove/Oven Laminate Hardwood Flooring Central Air and Heating Private Balcony Dishwasher Tiled Bathroom and Kitchen Floor Refrigerator * Certain amenities are only available in select apartments The building amenities include the following features: Recycling Courtyard Laundry Facilities BBQ/Grill Area Elevator EV Charging Station Garage Roof Terrace and Sundeck Controlled Access Assigned Parking Disclaimer: Photos may not be of the exact apartment available and are intended to provide a general representation of the unit. Floor plans and square footages 