        "mainpic": "96f5f560-6fc2-4134-8fd7-c76b23f30af5",
        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Viewing by appointment only. Flexible Lease Terms Available. 2 bedroom 2 bath apartment in great Westwood location. 1441 Midvale Avenue Westwood, Los Angeles, California, 90024 This 2 bedroom offers the following features: Stove & Oven Granite Countertops Private Balcony Tile Flooring Dishwasher Refrigerator Central Air/Heat * Certain amenities are only available in select apartments The building amenities include the following features: Fitness Center Garage Laundry Facilities Assigned Parking Spa Elevator Sauna BBQ/Grill Area EV Charging Station Controlled Access This 2 bedroom apartment features central air/heat, private balcony. Kitchen is equipped with a stove, oven, dishwasher and a refrigerator. Midvale Towers is a chic apartment community located in Westwood, Los Angeles. We offer contemporary Studio, 1 and 2 bedroom floor plans designed with your needs in mind. Nestled South of Wilshire Blvd., you are in close proximity to UCLA, UCLA Medical Center, and Century City. Treat yourself to everyday conveniences immediately outside your front door like Bristol Farms, Sprouts Farmers Market, Ralphs, Target, Trader Joe’s and 99 Ranch Market. Curious about living at Midvale Towers? Book an in-person or virtual tour today with one of our friendly and knowledgeable leasing associates. Underground parking included and storage available. For appointment or for questions, call today at show contact info . or visit http://www.MidvaleTowers.com. Disclaimer: Photos may not be of the exact apartment available and are intended to provide a general representation of the unit. Floor plans and square footages displayed are approximations and may vary between individual units. Rental rates, availability, lease terms, deposits, apartment features, amenities and specials are subject to change without notice. Terms may fluctuate based on qualifying standards.",
