        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Flexible Lease Terms Available. Modern designs, elegant finishes, and upscale amenities are waiting for you at Midvale Towers. Our apartments in Westwood come in studio, one-, and two-bedroom layouts that are spacious and adaptable. This Westwood 1 bedroom 1 bath apartment has all wood flooring, gas fireplace and quartz countertops. Kitchen is equipped with appliances including a refrigerator, a gas stove/oven, a microwave and a dishwasher. A variety of interior luxuries adorn them including air conditioning, a balcony, stainless steel appliances, and more. As a resident of our community, you will also have exclusive access to on-site laundry facilities, fitness center, and sauna and spa among other life-enhancing amenities. Midvale Towers’s location allows you to lead the lifestyle you have always envisioned. With easy access to Westwood Blvd and Wilshire Blvd, you are never far from all the shopping, dining, and entertainment nearby downtown Santa Monica has to offer. Escape to Westfield Century City or spend time exploring Westwood Park, knowing unapparelled rest and relaxation are waiting for you at home. Nestled South of Wilshire Blvd., our apartments are also near UCLA, UCLA Medical Center, and Century City. Here, you can treat yourself to everyday conveniences immediately outside your front door, like Bristol Farms, Sprouts Farmers Market, Ralphs, Target, Trader Joe’s and 99 Ranch Market. For appointment or for questions, call us at show contact info or visit http://www.MidvaleTowers.com . 1441 Midvale Avenue Westwood, Los Angeles, California, 90024 Brentwood, West LA, Beverly Hills This 1 bedroom apartment offers the following features: Central Air Microwave Private Balcony Refrigerator All Wood Flooring Quartz Countertops Gas Stove & Oven Air Conditioning Dishwasher * Certain amenities are only available in select apartments The building amenities include the following features: Elevator BBQ/Grill Area Assig