        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 2735 E 6th St, Los Angeles, CA 90023 Discover a new collection of thoughtfully crafted lofts, where elevated design and everyday affordability finally meet. These light‑filled spaces blend clean architectural lines, soaring ceilings, and contemporary finishes to create a home that feels both inspiring and effortlessly livable. With the Downtown LA Arts District just across the iconic Sixth Street Viaduct Bridge, you’re perfectly positioned to tap into the city’s most exciting creative, culinary, and cultural scenes—while enjoying the neighborhood charm and authenticity that make Boyle Heights one of Los Angeles’ most dynamic communities. Apartment Features: Polished concrete Stainless steel convection cooking REFRIGERATOR Stainless steel MICROWAVE Community Features: On-site manager offers customer service and help with maintenance EXCLUSIVE BBQ AREA CONTROLLED ACCESS Pedestrian key and vehicle clicker access Host some friends for some outdoor food and fun Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://liveoropropertiesla.com/bmobkpt2/step Pricing and availability are subject to change. Photos may not be of exact unit.",
