        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Flexible Lease Terms Available. Westwood 2 bedroom 2 bath with in-unit washer/dryer and more! Close to UCLA! 962 Hilgard Ave Westwood, Los Angeles, CA 90024 Near UCLA, Brentwood, West LA, Beverly Hills This 2 bedroom offers the following amenities: Laminate Flooring In The Living Room Ceramic Tiles Central Air/Heating Gas Range/Oven Plush Carpeting In The Bedrooms Granite Countertops Dishwasher Private Balcony In-Unit Washer/Dryer Cozy Gas Fireplace * Certain amenities are only available in select apartments Chateau Hilgard is a charming apartment community located in Westwood, Los Angeles. We offer well-appointed 1 and 2 bedroom floor plans designed with your needs in mind. Nestled North of Wilshire Blvd., you are in close proximity to UCLA, UCLA Medical Center, and Century City. Treat yourself to everyday conveniences immediately outside your front door like Whole Foods, Ralphs, Target, Trader Joe’s, and the weekly Farmers Market. This 2 bedroom 2 bath apartment has central air/heat, a gas fireplace, a private balcony, in-unit washer/dryer, and a gourmet kitchen equipped with granite countertops, a gas stove/oven, a refrigerator and a dishwasher. Living room has laminate flooring throughout, with plush carpeting in the bedrooms, beautiful ceramic tiles in entryway, kitchen and bathrooms. Community features include rooftop spa, roof terrace with BBQ/grill area and covered parking. Curious about living at Chateau Hilgard? Book an in-person or virtual tour today with one of our friendly and knowledgeable leasing associates. Call show contact info or visit http://www.Chateauhilgard.com. The building amenities include the following features: Roof Terrace Controlled Access BBQ/Grill Area Resort-Style Spa Assigned Parking Elevator Disclaimer: Photos may not be of the exact apartment available and are intended to provide a general representation of the unit. Floor plans and square footages displayed are approximations and may vary between individual units. Rental rates, availability, lease terms, deposits, apartment features, amenities and specials are subject to change without notice. Terms may fluctuate based on qualifying standards.",
