        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Flexible Lease Terms Available. Spacious Westwood Spacious 1 Bedroom 1 Bath Apartment. Westwood 1 bedroom and 1 bath is located minutes away from popular Westside locations, just south of Wilshire and one block west of Westwood Boulevard, we are close to Century City, Brentwood and Beverly Hills as well as the Santa Monica beaches, 3rd Street Promenade, Santa Monica Place, Main Street, Montana Avenue, Venice Beach, The Grove, Melrose Ave and many other great L.A. spots. Features include central air and heat, a gas fire place, a private balcony and more. Kitchen is fully equipped with quartz countertops, a refrigerator, a dishwasher, a gas range and an oven. Community features include covered parking, an elevator, a garage, a fitness center, a laundry facility, and a pool on the roof of our community. Parking included and extra storage available. Call us today at show contact info or apply at http://www.midvalecourt.com/. To view our full listings, visit http://www.siltongroup.com 1400 Midvale Avenue Westwood, Los Angeles, California, 90024 Brentwood, West LA, Beverly Hills This 1 bedroom offers the following amenities: Quartz Countertops Private Balcony Refrigerator Gas Range and Oven Dishwasher Central Air and Heat Gas Fireplace * Certain amenities are only available in select apartments The building amenities include the following features: Controlled Access Business Center Garage Fitness Center BBQ/Grill Area Laundry Facilities Assigned Parking Elevator Roof Terrace Disclaimer: Photos may not be of the exact apartment available and are intended to provide a general representation of the unit. Floor plans and square footages displayed are approximations and may vary between individual units. Rental rates, availability, lease terms, deposits, apartment features, amenities and specials are subject to change without notice. Terms may fluctuate based on qualifying standards.",
