        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Flexible Lease Terms Available. Westwood 3 Bedroom 3 Bathroom Apartment. Close To Everything! 3 bedroom apartment offers the following amenities: Microwave Cozy Gas Fireplace Dishwasher Central Air/Heating Cable Available Refrigerator Stove and Oven Tile Flooring * Certain amenities are only available in select apartments Community Amenities: Assigned Parking Elevator BBQ/Grill Area Laundry Facilities Sauna Pool Controlled Access Roof Terrace Fitness Center EV Charging Stations This apartment features wood flooring with a gas fireplace, private balcony, and central air/heat. Kitchen is equipped with appliances including a dishwasher, a gas stove, and a refrigerator. Community features include a swimming pool, a fitness center and gorgeous panoramic views of the Westwood skyline. We are perfectly situated in a very cosmopolitan neighborhood, our convenient location puts you within walking distance of everything in Westwood Village, just one block south of Wilshire and one block west of Westwood Boulevard. Call us at show contact info or apply at http://www.AshtonTowers.com. For more property photos, floor plans and further details visit: http://www.AshtonTowers.com 10930 Ashton Avenue Los Angeles, CA 90024 Disclaimer: Photos may not be of the exact apartment available and are intended to provide a general representation of the unit. Floor plans and square footages displayed are approximations and may vary between individual units. Rental rates, availability, lease terms, deposits, apartment features, amenities and specials are subject to change without notice. Terms may fluctuate based on qualifying standards.",
