        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Flexible Lease Terms Available. Spacious And Bright 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath Apartment In Prime Westwood Location Close To UCLA! 972 Hilgard Avenue Westwood, Los Angeles, California, 90024 Near UCLA, Brentwood, West LA, Beverly Hills 2 bedroom apartment offers the following amenities: Wood Flooring Granite Countertops Stove Dishwasher Microwave Refrigerator Central Air And Heating * Certain amenities are only available in select apartments Welcome to The Hilgard, your dream community where comfort, leisure, and entertainment are designed with your lifestyle in mind. With a prime location near UCLA and top-tier amenities, our apartments for rent in Westwood have everything you need to feel right at home. The Hilgard reaches new heights in apartment living with contemporary features uniquely designed to create a carefree and relaxing lifestyle. We offer apartments that combine charming style with attractive amenities that you will surely appreciate. This 2 bedroom 2 bath apartment features spacious living areas perfect for entertaining, with air conditioning and wood flooring throughout. Granite countertops in bathrooms and kitchen. Experience a carefree, relaxing lifestyle at The Hilgard. Perfectly situated in a very cosmopolitan neighborhood, The Hilgard is the ideal place to call home! Our convenient location puts you within walking distance of everything in Westwood Village, just two blocks north of Wilshire and one block east of Westwood Boulevard, exactly where you want. For more information, call us today at show contact info ! For more apartments, visit http://www.TheHilgard.com. The building amenities include the following features: EV Charging Station Controlled Access Garage Laundry Facilities Assigned Parking Elevator Roof Terrace and Sundeck BBQ/Grill Area Courtyard Recycling Disclaimer: Photos may not be of the exact apartment available and are intended to provide a general representation of the unit. Floor plans and square footages displayed are approximations and may vary between individual units. Rental rates, availability, lease terms, deposits, apartment features, amenities and specials are subject to change without notice. Terms may fluctuate based on qualifying standards.",
