      "house_ger": {
        "id": "44e65d18-1952-4b31-b4d2-2edc70528d87",
        "name": "Westwood Studio 1BA Near UCLA. w/ Fireplace/Balcony/Kitchen+More",
        "location": "972 Hilgard Ave near Weyburn Ave",
        "mainpic": "a768bd06-605d-4d33-a1d1-8a051c3866ee",
        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Flexible Lease Terms Available. Studio Apartment in Prime Westwood Location. Close to UCLA! 972 Hilgard Avenue Westwood, Los Angeles, California, 90024 Brentwood, West LA, Beverly Hills This Studio apartment offers the following amenities: Private Balcony Dishwasher Refrigerator Central Air and Heating Cozy Gas Fireplace Closets Stove and Microwave Hardwood Flooring Gated Parking * Certain amenities are only available in select apartments Community Amenities: Recycling Laundry Facilities Courtyard Garage Controlled Access BBQ/Grill Area Elevator Roof Terrace and Sundeck EV Charging Station Assigned Parking This Westwood Studio apartment features laminate flooring, a balcony, fireplace, central air conditioning/heat and more. Kitchen features a gas stove/oven, dishwasher, microwave and refrigerator. 972 Hilgard Avenue is a beautiful 40 unit apartment-complex centrally located in Westwood, a cosmopolitan, vibrant, and diverse community on the westside of Los Angeles, California. Perfectly situated in a very cosmopolitan neighborhood, The Hilgard is the ideal place to call home! Our convenient location puts you within walking distance of everything in Westwood Village, just two blocks north of Wilshire and one block east of Westwood Boulevard. Minutes away to all popular westside destinations including Armand Hammer Museum of Art & Cultural Center, UCLA, Getty Museum, Geffen Playhouse, Wadsworth Theatre. Fabulous restaurants and shopping, movie theatres, world class yoga, and public transportation are all at your fingertips. We are close to Century City, Brentwood and Beverly Hills as well as the Santa Monica beaches, 3rd Street Promenade, Santa Monica Place, Main Street, Montana Avenue, Venice Beach, The Grove, Melrose Ave and many other great L.A. spots. Our residents enjoy some of the best community amenities available anywhere. Take advantage of several public parks nearby or enjoy our picnic area with barbecues. For questions or appointment, call us at show contact info or visit http://www.TheHilgard.com. Disclaimer: Photos may not be of the exact apartment available and are intended to provide a general representation of the unit. Floor plans and square footages displayed are approximations and may vary between individual units. Rental rates, availability, lease terms, deposits, apartment features, amenities and specials are subject to change without notice. Terms may fluctuate based on qualifying standards.",
