        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Flexible Lease Terms Available. Top Floor 2 Bedroom 2 Bath Penthouse Loft Apartment Close To Everything Westwood. Close To UCLA. 972 Hilgard Avenue Westwood, Los Angeles, California, 90024 Brentwood, West LA, Beverly Hills Top floor 2 bedroom penthouse loft apartment offers the following features: Refrigerator Carpeted Bedrooms Mirrored Closet Doors Central Air/Heating Private Balcony Dishwasher Laminate Flooring Tile Entryway, Kitchen And Bathroom Floors Microwave Cozy Gas Fireplace * Certain amenities are only available in select apartments Community Amenities: Recycling Garage Assigned Parking BBQ/Grill Area Elevator Controlled Access Roof Terrace and Sundeck Courtyard Laundry Facilities EV Charging Station This top floor 2 bedroom penthouse loft apartment is located within walking distance of everything in Westwood Village, just two blocks north of Wilshire and one block east of Westwood Boulevard, exactly where you want. Features include spacious living areas, with a cozy gas fireplace, laminate floors, carpeted bedrooms, central air/heat, a private balcony, tile floors in bathrooms, kitchen and entryway. Kitchen is fully equipped with granite countertops, a refrigerator, a dishwasher, a microwave, and a gas stove. With our dedicated maintenance department, you’ll have more opportunities to enjoy life! Take advantage of several public parks nearby or enjoy our picnic area with barbecues. Call us today at show contact info ! Our wonderful staff is looking forward to serving you with excellence. To apply or for more information, visit our website at http://www.TheHilgard.com Disclaimer: Photos may not be of the exact apartment available and are intended to provide a general representation of the unit. Floor plans and square footages displayed are approximations and may vary between individual units. Rental rates, availability, lease terms, deposits, apartment features, amenities and specials are subject to change without notice. Terms may fluctuate based on qualifying standards.",
