        "geocode_query": "964 Hilgard Ave near Weyburn Ave",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Flexible Lease Terms Available. Westwood 2 Bedroom 2 Bath Apartment with Stainless Steel Appliances. 964 Hilgard Avenue Westwood, Los Angeles, California, 90024 Brentwood, West LA, Beverly Hills 2 bedroom apartment offers the following features: Dishwasher Tiled Kitchen And Baths With Granite Countertops Refrigerator Gas Range And Oven Stainless Steel Appliances Central Heat Microwave * Certain amenities are only available in select apartments Community Amenities: Assigned Parking Laundry Facilities BBQ/Grill Area Great Westwood Location Controlled Access Unique vintage garden-style apartment in a small building reminiscent of true Westwood living in the very best location near UCLA. This very spacious and renovated 2-bedroom 2-bath apartment has large picture windows that look out into a gorgeous landscaped courtyard. The extra-large kitchen has all stainless steel appliances including gas stove and oven, dishwasher, microwave, and refrigerator with generous granite countertops and updated maple cabinetry. Separate dining room area opens to a sizeable living room with rich wood flooring and the bedrooms have generous closet space, and windows. The 2 bedrooms are equipped with plush carpeting, master bedroom includes large walk-in closets. Bathrooms have granite countertops and updated cabinetry with shower/tub combo and dual vanities located in guest bathroom and walk-in shower in master bathroom. Best of all -- you have a closed garage for sizeable storage needs as well as tandem parking behind it which allows for that most-needed commodity in Westwood -- parking. We are literally one block from UCLA on the east side of campus which gives incredible access to Westwood Village and UCLA without the noise that is common on the west side of school. Walk one block to Trader Joe's, Target, and the largest Ralph's in Los Angeles with an amazing food court, with all the accompanying features of the Village at extremely close proximity. This is a one-of-a-kind apartment for someone who wants both character and quality in their apartment. This building is under rent control. For more information, call us at show contact info or apply at our website: http://www.westwoodgarden.com/ Disclaimer: Photos may not be of the exact apartment available and are intended to provide a general representation of the unit. Floor plans and square footages displayed are approximations and may vary between individual units. Rental rates, availability, lease terms, deposits, apartment features, amenities and specials are subject to change without notice. Terms may fluctuate based on qualifying standards.",
