        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 18601 Hatteras St, Tarzana, CA 91356 With its beautiful landscape, Tarzana Terrace has so much to offer, such as a relaxing swimming pool, community clubhouse and well-equipped fitness center. Our spacious two- and three-bedroom apartments are all you could ever dream of, offering patios, vaulted ceilings, walk-in closets and more. Our community is located in the heart of the San Fernando Valley, with easy access to the 101 freeway. We are conveniently located near the ever-popular Ventura Boulevard, featuring markets, dining, and a wide variety of retail shopping. Stop by and take a tour, and make Tarzana Terraces your new home! Features Include: Gated Community Pet Friendly BBQ/Picnic Area Laundry Facility Sparkling Pool Clubhouse Swimming Pool Fitness Center Cable Ready Pet-Friendly Community Assigned ParkingContact our office for pricing and details Contact our office for pricing and details Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livegkmanagement.com/ju4lvuhv/tarzana-terraces Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit. Contact us today for the most up to date information.",
