        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Flexible Lease Terms Available. Top floor 3 bedroom 3 bath penthouse apartment in the heart of Westwood, call today! 3 bedroom penthouse apartment offers the following amenities: Plush Carpeting In The Bedrooms Extra High Vaulted Ceilings Dishwasher Rich Wood Flooring In The Living Room Cozy Gas Fireplace Cable Available Quartz Countertops Vertical Blinds Stove And Oven Microwave Central Air/Heating Refrigerator Ceramic Tile In Kitchen And Bathrooms Stainless Steel Appliances Ceramic Tile Entryway Mirrored Closet Doors * Certain amenities are only available in select apartments This 3 bedroom, 3 bath penthouse apartment is a corner unit with extra-high ceilings and gorgeous views across the city, it has rich wood flooring in the living room, plush carpeting in all bedrooms with vanity in the master bedroom. Gourmet kitchen is equipped with quartz countertops, all stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher, a gas stove, and a refrigerator. Beautiful ceramic tile in entryway, kitchen and bathrooms. Our residents are offered full access to all our exquisite community amenities. From the solar heated swimming pool, fitness center and gorgeous panoramic views of the Westwood skyline, you'll find easy living with endless comforts and conveniences here at Ashton Towers. Nestled just South of Wilshire Blvd., you are in close proximity to UCLA, UCLA Medical Center, and Century City. Treat yourself to everyday conveniences immediately outside your front door like Bristol Farms, Sprouts Farmers Market, Ralphs, Target, Trader Joe’s and 99 Ranch Market. For appointment or for questions, call us at show contact info . For more property photos, floor plans and further details visit: http://www.AshtonTowers.com Community Amenities: Laundry Facilities BBQ/Grill Area Fitness Center Pool Controlled Access Roof Terrace Assigned Parking Sauna Elevator 10930 Ashton Avenue Westwood, Los Angeles, California, 90024 Near UCLA, Brentwood, West LA, Beverly Hills Disclaimer: Photos may not be of the exact apartment available and are intended to provide a general representation of the unit. Floor plans and square footages displayed are approximations and may vary between individual units. Rental rates, availability, lease terms, deposits, apartment features, amenities and specials are subject to change without notice. Terms may fluctuate based on qualifying standards.",
