        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Flexible Lease Terms Available. Walk to UCLA. Spacious 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath Apartment in Prime Westwood Location. 972 Hilgard Avenue Westwood, Los Angeles, California, 90024 Brentwood, West LA, Beverly Hills 1 bedroom apartment offers the following amenities: Refrigerator Tile Floors Microwave Dishwasher Wood Flooring In The Living Room Carpeted Bedroom Central Air And Heating Stove * Certain amenities are only available in select apartments The building amenities include the following features: EV Charging Station Controlled Access Laundry Facilities Garage BBQ/Grill Area Courtyard Elevator Recycling Roof Terrace and Sundeck Assigned Parking This west facing apartment features spacious living areas perfect for entertaining, a breakfast bar, air conditioning, wood flooring in the living room, carpeted bedroom, tile flooring in the bathroom, kitchen and entryway. Kitchen is equipped with appliances including a stove, a refrigerator, a microwave and a dishwasher. All apartments feature central air conditioning and heating, with most having stainless steel appliances and private balconies, while our on-site management and maintenance teams ensure a seamless living experience. Beyond your front door, enjoy community perks like a BBQ/grill area, laundry facilities, and a rooftop terrace perfect for relaxation. Nestled north of Wilshire Blvd. and near Weyburn Avenue, The Hilgard places you in close proximity to UCLA, UCLA Medical Center, and Century City. Call us today at show contact info or visit our website at http://www.TheHilgard.com. Disclaimer: Photos may not be of the exact apartment available and are intended to provide a general representation of the unit. Floor plans and square footages displayed are approximations and may vary between individual units. Rental rates, availability, lease terms, deposits, apartment features, amenities and specials are subject to change without notice. Terms may fluctuate based on qualifying standards.",
