        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Flexible Lease Terms Available! Large Top Floor 2 Bedroom Penthouse Apartment With Extra-high Ceilings. Prime Westwood! Available January! Unrivaled quality, endless comforts, and gracious apartment living. This large top floor 2 bedroom penthouse corner unit features extra-high ceilings, central air/heat, and a cozy fireplace. Beautiful ceramic tiles in entryway, kitchen and bathroom floors. Kitchen is equipped with quartz countertops, appliances include a microwave, a dishwasher, a gas stove/oven and a refrigerator. Our apartment homes are thoughtfully detailed with lavish amenities including covered parking, an elevator, a garage, fitness center, a laundry facility, and a pool on the roof of our community. For appointment to see this apartment or for questions, call us at show contact info or apply at http://www.MidvaleCourt.com 1400 Midvale Avenue Westwood, Los Angeles, California, 90024 Brentwood, West LA, Beverly Hills This 2 bedroom penthouse apartment offers the following features: Extra-high Ceilings Ceramic Tiles Central Air/Heating Gas Stove/Oven Refrigerator Cozy Gas Fireplace Dishwasher * Certain amenities are only available in select apartments Community Amenities: Garage Business Center Controlled Access Spa EV Charging Station Laundry Facilities Pool Study Lounge BBQ/Grill Area Elevator Roof Terrace Assigned Parking Stretch/Yoga room Fitness Center Sauna Disclaimer: Photos may not be of the exact apartment available and are intended to provide a general representation of the unit. Floor plans and square footages displayed are approximations and may vary between individual units. Rental rates, availability, lease terms, deposits, apartment features, amenities and specials are subject to change without notice. Terms may fluctuate based on qualifying standards.",
