        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Flexible Lease Terms Available! Call For More Details! Top Floor 4 Bedroom, 2 Bath Penthouse Apartment In Westwood Village, 1 Block from UCLA. 972 Hilgard Avenue Westwood, Los Angeles, California, 90024 Brentwood, West LA, Beverly Hills Welcome to The Hilgard, your dream community where comfort, leisure, and entertainment are designed with your lifestyle in mind. With a prime location near UCLA and top-tier amenities, our apartments in Westwood, Los Angeles, have everything you need to feel right at home. All apartments feature central air conditioning and heating, with most having stainless steel appliances and private balconies, while our on-site management and maintenance teams ensure a seamless living experience. Beyond your front door, enjoy community perks like a BBQ/grill area, laundry facilities, and a rooftop terrace perfect for relaxation. Nestled north of Wilshire Blvd. and near Weyburn Avenue, The Hilgard places you in close proximity to UCLA, UCLA Medical Center, and Century City. Step outside your door and enjoy everyday conveniences like Whole Foods, Ralphs, Target, and Trader Joe’s, along with the vibrant Westwood Village Farmers' Market. When it’s time to unwind, explore top dining, shopping, and entertainment destinations, including Bruin Theatre and Broxton Brewery & Public House. Plus, with major employers like UCLA and Bank of America nearby, commuting is effortless. For a touch of nature, visit the UCLA Botanical Garden and immerse yourself in a serene outdoor escape. For appointment or for questions, call us at show contact info . To apply or for more information, visit http://www.TheHilgard.com This 4 bedroom penthouse apartment offers the following amenities: Cozy Gas Fireplace Cable Ready Dishwasher Granite Countertops Refrigerator Laminate/Carpet Flooring Tile Floors Private Balcony Central Air/Heating Stove/Oven * Certain amenities are only available in select apartments The building amenities include the following features: BBQ/Grill Area Laundry Facilities Controlled Access Assigned Parking Recycling EV Charging Station Courtyard Garage Roof Terrace and Sundeck Elevator Disclaimer: Photos may not be of the exact apartment available and are intended to provide a general representation of the unit. Floor plans and square footages displayed are approximations and may vary between individual units. Rental rates, availability, lease terms, deposits, apartment features, amenities and specials are subject to change without notice. Terms may fluctuate based on qualifying standards.",
