        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Flexible Lease Terms Available. Bright And Spacious Top Floor Studio Penthouse Apartment In Westwood. Close To Everything. 10930 Ashton Avenue Westwood, Los Angeles, California, 90024 Brentwood, West LA, Beverly Hills Studio penthouse apartment offers the following amenities: Cable Available Dishwasher Stove And Oven Microwave Central Air/Heating Refrigerator * Certain amenities are only available in select apartments Welcome to Ashton Towers, where sophisticated living meets the vibrant energy of Westwood. Nestled at 10930 Ashton Avenue in one of Los Angeles' most sought-after neighborhoods, this luxury apartment community redefines what it means to call Westwood home. Whether you're drawn to our thoughtfully designed studios or seeking the spaciousness of our three-bedroom residences, each floor plan reflects a commitment to modern elegance and comfort. This top floor studio penthouse apartment is located within walking distance of everything in Westwood Village. Features include a private balcony, laminate wood and tile floors, a kitchen equipped with a gas stove and oven, a dishwasher, and a refrigerator. Our community features a solar heated swimming pool, fitness center and gorgeous panoramic views of the Westwood skyline, you'll find easy living with endless comforts and conveniences here at Ashton Towers. We pride ourselves on ensuring residents only the best in apartment living. For appointment or for questions, call us at show contact info or visit http://www.AshtonTowers.com to apply. Community Amenities: Pool EV Charging Stations Assigned Parking Fitness Center BBQ/Grill Area Laundry Facilities Sauna Elevator Controlled Access Roof Terrace Disclaimer: Photos may not be of the exact apartment available and are intended to provide a general representation of the unit. Floor plans and square footages displayed are approximations and may vary between individual units. Rental rates, availability, lease terms, deposits, apartment features, amenities and specials are subject to change without notice. Terms may fluctuate based on qualifying standards.",
