        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 3767 Clarington Ave, Los Angeles, CA 90034 Bedrooms:  0 Bathrooms:  1 Square Feet:  625 Rent Price:  2405 Located just north of Culver City, in the vibrant Palms District, Clarington Apartments offers the best of Los Angeles at your doorstep. Whether you’re a foodie, an art lover or have an affinity for shopping, the Palms district has it all. Enjoy the latest film release at the Culver Theater, grab a bite to eat at Versailles Cuban Restaurant and end the day with a scoop of small-batch ice cream from Salt & Straw - we recommend the honey lavender. Easy access to the Palm stop on Metro E line, the 10 and 405 freeways keep you connected to all of Los Angeles – making your Santa Monica, Downtown LA, or Brentwood commute a breeze. With flexibility at our forefront, Clarington offers short-term leases designed to fit your needs and lifestyle. Professionally Managed by Cirrus Asset Management, Inc., CA - License # 01834798 Amenities Include: Controlled Access/Gated Air Conditioner Ceiling Fan Wi-Fi Lounge Large Closets Pool Free Weights Carpeting Elevator Fireplace Window Coverings Refrigerator Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://cirrusmgmt.com/t3ulsok5/clarington-apartments Pricing and availability are subject to change.",
