        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post 3610 S. Nogales St, West Covina, CA 91792 Walnut Ridge prides itself on offering a tranquil and relaxing atmosphere to its residents by creating the perfect place for the special things in life. Surrounded by lush landscaping and enhanced by strikingly beautiful grounds, our studio, one- and two-bedroom living spaces are bright and expansive. Come experience an empowering workout in our fitness center, or if relaxation is the name of the game, unwind poolside or indulge in our hot tub. At Walnut Ridge, you will find all the amenities and features designed for easy living. Our community places you near parks, trails, schools, shopping centers, theaters and many delectable dining options. For your convenience, we are also walking distance to public transportation and provide easy freeway access. Serene living is waiting for you at Walnut Ridge. Features Include: Contact our office for pricing and details 2 Jacuzzis Laundry Facilities 2 Swimming Pools Assigned Cover CarportContact our office for pricing and details Barbecue Grilling Area Playground Fitness Center Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livegkmanagement.com/4yiowwxa/walnut-ridge Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit. Contact us today for the most up to date information.",
