        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post 300 N Beaudry Ave, Los Angeles, CA 90012 Move-In Today! Luxury studio, one, and two-bedroom apartments for rent in the heart of DTLA. Ferrante is a luxury resort-style community that guarantees exceeding all your expectations. Just minutes away from the Financial District, bringing you closer to well-known art museums, fine dining, culture, and historical sights, all tailored to your needs right outside your front door. Community Features: Large Lobby with Wall Fountain, Illuminated Art, Coffee Bar, Waiting Areas, and Adjacent Lounge Rooftop Decks with Lounge Seating and BBQ Facilities 3 Swimming Pools and Spa Areas with Private Seating and Fabric Cabanas Stainless Steel BBQ Islands with Outdoor Dining Areas Outdoor Fire Pits and Lounge Areas Large Conference Room 3 Large Gyms with Cardio, Strength, and Pilates Area Karaoke Room Men's and Women's Changing Rooms with Steam Shower and Sauna Personal Business Center Library Movie Theater Indoor Regulation Basketball Court with Provisions for Indoor Volleyball and Balcony Overlook Indoor Regulation Pickleball Court Individual Resident Bicycle Racks and Fill/Repair Station Secondary Entrance Lobby with Adjacent Video Game Arcade, Table Games, and Wine Cellar Speakeasy Lounge Lounge with Kitchenette Some Units Have Private Street-level Entries Lush On-site Landscape and Decorative Feature Fountains Outdoor Sand Volleyball Court Call: show contact info WEBSITE https://liveghp.com/vp5bwrvj/ferrante Pricing and availability are subject to change.",
