        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 2100 S. Lark Ellen Ave, West Covina, CA 91792 Windwood Apartments prides itself on offering a tranquil and relaxing atmosphere to its residents by creating the perfect place for the special things in life. Surrounded by lush landscaping and enhanced by beautiful grounds, our one-, two- and three-bedroom living spaces are bright and expansive. Come experience an empowering workout in our fitness center, and full-size basketball court and tennis courts. If relaxation is the name of the game, unwind poolside and indulge in our spa. At Windwood, you will find all the amenities and features designed for easy living. Our community is located near Woodgrove Park, Big League Dreams Sports Park, local shopping centers, and is minutes from the 10 and 60 freeways. Tranquil living is waiting for you at Windwood Apartments, so give us a call today to schedule your tour. Features Include: Laundry Facility On-Site Shaker Cabinetry Upgrade Lighting Package Quartz Counter Top Tennis Court Pool Fitness Center Basketball Court Playground Stainless Appliance Package Assigned ParkingContact our office for pricing and details Outdoor Hot Tub Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livegkmanagement.com/y7p4zzkx/windwood-apartments Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit. Contact us today for the most up to date information.",
