        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post 3330 East Foothill Boulevard, Pasadena, CA 91107 Bell Pasadena offers you studio, one-, and two-bedroom homes with upscale features and lifestyle amenities that make each day feel effortless. From designer finishes to vibrant community spaces, everything is built for comfort and connection. Located next to the Metro Gold Line and minutes from Old Town Pasadena, Caltech, and Huntington Hospital, this is luxury living in the center of it all. Inside your apartment, experience modern convenience with stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and espresso cabinetry. Select layouts include large kitchen islands and private balconies, while walk-in closets and in-unit storage keep things organized. Every home includes a full-size washer and dryer to make daily routines easier. Life at Bell Pasadena flows naturally from activity to relaxation. Start your day in the cardio theater, meet friends by the cushy outdoor fireplace, or unwind beside the resort-inspired pool. Work from the Wi-Fi café, charge your EV onsite, or grab a bite at the Minnow food pod. You can enjoy dramatic mountain views, store your bike with ease, and treat your pet at the onsite spa. With outdoor grills, a modern clubhouse, and 24-hour package lockers, home extends far beyond your front door. Bell Pasadena also provides 24-hour emergency maintenance and walkable access to restaurants, grocery stores, and retail. Some apartment features may vary. Please contact our leasing team for full availability. Apartment Features: Large Kitchen Islands* Walk-in Closets* Dramatic Views of the San Gabriel Mountains Private Balconies* In-unit Storage Resort-inspired Pool Modern Clubhouse Social Lounge Designer Espresso Cabinets Community Features: View Image Dramatic Views of the San Gabriel Mountains 24-Hour Accessible Package Lockers View Image Poolside Umbrellas View Image Wi-Fi Café View Image Electric Vehicle Charging Stations View Image Cushy Outdoor Fireplace wi