        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 123 S. Figueroa St, Los Angeles, CA 90012 Welcome to Promenade Towers, your welcoming haven that opens the door to the very best of Los Angeles living. Our downtown LA apartments provide a gateway to the world-class entertainment venues and iconic landmarks that define the heart of DTLA. Inside each spacious residence, modern conveniences seamlessly blend with attractive finishes, ensuring a truly carefree living experience. Discover the allure of our high-rise buildings, offering not only pet-friendly floor plans but also a range of amenities. From a sparkling outdoor swimming pool to a state-of-the-art fitness center, our community is designed to elevate your lifestyle. Immerse yourself in lush landscapes, and let the 24-hour attended lobby create a resort-like ambiance right at home. Conveniently located just off I-110, our prime address puts you within easy reach of picturesque parks, popular restaurants, and renowned museums—all within walking distance. Experience it all firsthand by visiting us at Promenade Towers today. Your ideal home in the heart of Los Angeles awaits. Features Include: EV Charging Stations BBQ Grills Fitness Center Recreation Room Resort-Style Pool And Spa 24-Hour Lobby Attendants ParkingContact our office for pricing and details Parking Available Contact our office for pricing and details Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livegkmanagement.com/sdtwutzd/promenade-tower Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit. Contact us today for the most up to date information.",
