        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 1415 N. San Gabriel Blvd, Rosemead, CA 91770 San Gabriel Villa is located in the city of Rosemead and is just a hop, skip and a jump from Pasadena, where you'll find a variety of historical places to experience and explore, such as the Miltimore House, Adobe Flores and the Rialto Theatre. This program offers educational and fun activities including field trips, movies and much more. If kicking back is more your style, then you'll love our charmingly spacious two-bedroom or three-bedroom apartment homes, overflowing with natural light. Relax and rejuvenate in one of our courtyards or join a pickup game on the basketball court or gather with friends in the barbecue and picnic area. We have a little something for everyone. San Gabriel Villa is the ideal place to call home. Features Include: Outdoor Fitness Area Online Rental Payments Two Playgrounds Laundry Facility Pet-Friendly Community Gated Electronic Entrance Gated ParkingContact our office for pricing and details Contact our office for pricing and details Basketball Court Close To Park Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livegkmanagement.com/b3azsb35/san-gabriel-villa Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit. Contact us today for the most up to date information.",
