        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post 2735 E 6th St, Los Angeles, CA 90023 Discover a new collection of thoughtfully crafted studio lofts, where elevated design and everyday affordability finally meet. These light‑filled spaces blend clean architectural lines, soaring ceilings, and contemporary finishes to create a home that feels both inspiring and effortlessly livable. With the Downtown LA Arts District just across the iconic Sixth Street Viaduct Bridge, you’re perfectly positioned to tap into the city’s most exciting creative, culinary, and cultural scenes—while enjoying the neighborhood charm and authenticity that make Boyle Heights one of Los Angeles’ most dynamic communities. Live in a space that inspires you, in a neighborhood that moves you. These studio lofts bring together the best of Eastside character and Downtown convenience—at a price that keeps LA living within reach. Apartment Features: IN-UNIT WASHER/DRYER MICROWAVE Stainless steel convection cooking POLISHED CONCRETE FLOORING Polished concrete Easy breeze when you want it Community Features: PROFESSIONAL ON-SITE MANAGEMENT Host some friends for some outdoor food and fun Exercise in a convenient, on-site gym CONTROLLED ACCESS EXCLUSIVE BBQ AREA Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://liveoropropertiesla.com/2cx5f62u/step Pricing and availability are subject to change. Photos may not be of exact unit.",
