        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Toluca Lake 2BR/2BA Brand New Inside a Mid-Century Classic $3,400/month available 8/1/26 4143 Warner Blvd, Burbank, CA 91505 Washer/dryer - dishwasher - central AC - semi private yard! Welcome to your stylish new home in the heart of Toluca Lake, just blocks from Warner Bros. Studios! This brand-new 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom unit blends the charm of 1950s architecture with modern upgrades perfect for creatives, commuters, and anyone who loves the best of both old and new. Features You'll Love: Mid-century bones, modern soul: Built in 1951, Brand-new interiors: Fresh wood floors, sleek new appliances, and a striking steel support beam running through the unit as a bold architectural statement. Bright + open layout with great natural light 2 full bathrooms and generous closet space Private entrance in a quiet, friendly building Prime Location with a Storied Backdrop: Nestled on Warner Blvd, & Rose Ave. you're in one of Burbank's most walkable and storied neighborhoods Toluca Lake, beloved by actors, animators, and musicians for generations. Just a few blocks to Warner Bros. Studios. Stroll to Trader Joe's, Whole Foods, and Riverside Drive, lined with charming boutiques and cafe culture Walk to local icons: Bob's Big Boy (1950s landmark diner) Hank's Bagels, Paty's, Coffee Commissary, and more: Sushi Yuzu, Veggie Grill, Something Vegan, Sharky's Quick access to the 134/101/5 freeways, Griffith Park, Universal Studios, and Studio City Quiet, tree-lined street with easy street permit parking. Thanks for looking!",
