        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post One Bedroom w/ New Appliances | Koreatown, Echo Park, Silver Lake & DTLA | 410 Lucas Avenue, C, Los Angeles, CA 90017 1595.00 / Month 1 BEDROOMS | 1 BATHROOMS Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6OTYyNDc3?property=2379931&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/410-lucas-avenue-los-angeles-ca-unit-c/aefce6a8-af7f-4dd2-b31e-f5fec1e7a4e0?source=craigslist Property Description: Inquiries | Email: show contact info Text or call: show contact info Current Availabilities: https://vf-developments.com/ * Please note: the advertised price of $1,595 is based off a $1,200 concession (applied upfront and all at once) being factored into the monthly base rent due of $1,695 (ONE THOUSAND SIX HUNDRED NINETY FIVE DOLLARS ) to show the savings. Carefully restored and designed by a renowned LA designer, these late 1950s modern luxury rental homes feature keyless entry door locks to spacious one and two-bedroom floor plans with newly renovated kitchen and bathrooms. The kitchen boasts sparkling white stone quartz countertops with brand new self-closing cabinetry and high-end stainless-steel refrigerators with matching gas cooktop with oven and microwave. iRing doorbells with a smart home video security camera are also included. There’s a community washer and dryer on site. Bathrooms feature porcelain tiled bath tubs and glass shower doors. Each rental home also includes central A/C cooling and heating with recessed lights with luxury style cellular shade window blinds and distressed wood plank floors. | EXTERIOR | - Newly Modernized Façade - City Approved & Completed Earthquake Seismic Retrofit - Keyless Electronic Entry | INTERIOR | - Cellular Shade Window Blinds - Spacious Designer Floor Plan - Vinyl Plank Flooring | KITCHEN | - Modern Designer Cabinetry - Quartz Countertops - Stainless-Steel Appliances - Refrigerator - Range w/ Oven - Mi